{
  "text": "Some clinicians prescribe these especially in patients who are prone to vasodilatory side effects and who are intolerant of other vasodilators. As with many other drugs used in RP, the evidence base is weak, with only one randomised trial which was open label [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "10234172"
